Instance Method# copyElementValues

DriverKitiOSiPadOSmacOS

```
IOReturn copyElementValues(int element_index, IOReportElementValues * elementValues);
```

## [ Parameters ](/documentation/driverkit/ioreporter_ivars/copyelementvalues#parameters)

`element_index`
- Index of the element to return values from

`elementValues`
- For returning the content of element values

## [Return Value](/documentation/driverkit/ioreporter_ivars/copyelementvalues#return-value)

Returns the content of an element

## [Discussion](/documentation/driverkit/ioreporter_ivars/copyelementvalues#discussion)

Copies the values of an internal element to *elementValues

For efficiently and thread-safely reading _elements. May need to find the index of the element first.

Locking: Caller must ensure that the reporter (data) lock is held.
